# EU-8 IR-recall results + ANN/IR synthesis

**Date:** 2026-05-31. **Status:** full-corpus run complete. **Companion to:**
`dev/plans/runs/0.7.2-PR-2c-recall-rootcause.md` (the ANN root-cause).

## What was run
- **ANN recall** (fidelity): `eu7_real_corpus_ac.rs`, corrected harness (NEW method:
  exclude query-source before top-10, dedup-GT), full corpus N=7667, K=192, real
  candle bge-small. Commit `a601d1c` (worktree `agent-af9f5a6ca35c0b19b`, branch
  `0.7.2-PR-2c-representative-pin`).
- **IR recall** (relevance): `eu8_ir_validation.rs`, full corpus 7667 docs + all 200
  chains, 301 labeled queries (`ground_truth_queries.expected_top_k_doc_ids`), real
  candle bge-small. Commit `5658d39` (worktree `agent-af07339f77147979f`, branch
  `worktree-agent-af07339f77147979f`). Raw: `dev/plans/runs/0.7.1-EU-8-measurements.json`.

## ANN recall (the fidelity signal) — confirmed
Same run, scoring method varied:
- **OLD** (exclude-after + set-GT, the original harness): **0.859** (CI 0.832-0.885, sigma 0.0137); target_in_top10 = 70/100.
- **NEW** (exclude-before + dedup-GT, standard ANN): **0.937** (CI 0.913-0.957, sigma 0.0116).
- **+7.8pp** is pure measurement-methodology artifact. NEW's full CI sits above the 0.90 floor.
- Latency AC-013 PASS (p50 36 / p99 49 ms). Stress AC-019 MISS (p99 1201 ms vs 499 bound) -- contention-inflated dev-box scouting, NOT a gate; re-run clean on an idle box.

## IR recall (the relevance signal) — full corpus, 301 queries
**Overall: recall@10 = 0.5714** (CI 0.530-0.614, sigma 0.0215), precision@10 = 0.162,
**MRR = 0.686**, NDCG@10 = 0.561; zero-hit queries 66/301; coverage 593/593 expected
ids present; duplicate_bodies = 428; unmapped_results = 0.

By relation type (the informative cut):

| relation | n | recall@10 | MRR | NDCG@10 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| action_from | 67 | **0.811** | 0.827 | 0.753 |
| follows_up_on | 66 | 0.626 | 0.926 | 0.665 |
| summarizes | 67 | 0.547 | 0.743 | 0.567 |
| mentions | 68 | 0.444 | 0.494 | 0.450 |
| contradicts | 33 | **0.288** | 0.201 | 0.178 |

By chain shape: `TODO->NOTE->EMAIL` 0.929 / `ARTICLE->NOTE->TODO` 0.859 /
`EMAIL->NOTE->TODO` 0.760 / `ARTICLE->NOTE->EMAIL` 0.444 / `EMAIL->MEETING->TODO`
0.323 / `MEETING->TODO->NOTE(contradicts)` 0.311.

## Synthesis (in the IR-vs-ANN framework)

| Signal | Value | Tests | Reading |
|---|---|---|---|
| ANN recall | **0.937** | index / sign-bit quantization fidelity (GT = exact f32 KNN, same model) | healthy; clears 0.90 floor |
| IR recall | **0.571** | embedder semantic relevance (GT = labeled relevant doc ids) | the ceiling; relation-dependent |

**ANN (0.937) exceeds IR (0.571) by +37pp.** By the standard rule (once ANN fidelity
exceeds the embedder's IR ceiling by ~15-20%, further index/quantization tuning yields
no perceptible user gain), the verdict is unambiguous:

- **The quantization is NOT the bottleneck.** It faithfully returns ~94% of the exact
  neighbors. Chasing ANN recall higher (bumping K / `TOP_K_BIT_CANDIDATES`, tighter
  index) is wasted compute.
- **The embedder/task is the ceiling.** The levers that move end-to-end quality are a
  better embedder (semantic) or **using the graph** for relation-following -- NOT the
  vector pipeline.

### Important caveats on the IR number
1. **Synthetic relationship task, not human qrels.** Chains are generated by
   `tests/corpus/scripts/generate_chain_corpus.py`. Some relations are *inherently
   wrong for pure vector search*: **contradicts** (0.29) -- a contradicting doc is not
   reliably *near* in embedding space; cosine cannot capture logical negation. Those
   relations are precisely what the engine's **graph edges** exist for, and EU-8 search
   deliberately does not traverse them. So the 0.571 understates pure-semantic
   retrieval: the similarity-friendly relations (action_from / follows_up_on /
   summarizes) average ~0.66.
2. **Duplicate-body mapping.** 428 dup bodies; the body->doc_id first-occurrence rule
   can map a content-correct retrieval to a different id than expected, modestly
   undercounting. Clean fix (same lesson as the ANN harness): have the engine search
   return doc ids, not just bodies.
3. Dev-box scouting (synthetic queries). Canonical relevance eval remains future work.

## Bottom line for the campaign
- **Quantization/ANN story: CLOSED.** Fidelity 0.937, 0.90 floor holds, no K-tuning warranted.
- **Embedder/IR story: OPENED.** Real, relation-dependent headroom; future work is
  semantic/graph, not quantization.
- **PR-2b (mean recompute) + PR-2c (representative pin): both confirmed to address a
  NON-problem for recall** (the mean moves real recall only +1.9pp; recall was never
  broken). Keep-vs-shelve decision: see `dev/plans/prompts/0.7.2-PR-2bc-reassessment.md`.

