    28	**Measured the standard ANN way (exclude the query-source doc BEFORE top-10,
    29	match GT by id/dedup), the engine's real recall@10 is ~0.93 — it CLEARS the 0.90
    30	floor.** PR-2b (mean recompute) and PR-2c (representative pin) are correctly
    31	engineered but address a non-problem for recall.
