    49	## The measure under discussion (so the numbers are interpretable)
    50	
    51	`recall@10` here is the **ANN / quantization-fidelity** flavor (FAISS / ANN-
    52	Benchmarks sense), NOT the IR-relevance sense:
    53	`recall@10 = |retrieved_top10 ∩ exact_f32_top10| / 10`, where ground truth = the
    54	exact top-10 by full-precision cosine over the SAME model, and retrieved = the
    55	sign-bit binary-quant (K=192 Hamming candidates) + f32 rerank pipeline. It
    56	measures how faithfully the lossy 1-bit index reproduces the brute-force
    57	neighbors — not whether results are "relevant". Percentile bootstrap (1000
    58	resamples, SEED=0xE0) for CIs throughout.
